=80=94drum roll=E2=80=94Will Lewis has decided to appoint Matt Murray as ex=
ecutive editor, but is waiting until after the new year to share the news w=
ith his staff. Plus, some new details on Mark Thompson=E2=80=99s impending =
CNN layoffs.

